{"tid":1124713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【維港會】「Airdrop劇透狂」出沒 向陌生人爆《復仇者4》劇情","createTime":"2019-04-25T07:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T11:03:32.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a0a2a7a5e7885ec23db85e30d6d5cf081d0979","tid":1124713,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"全球Marvel迷期待的《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers：Endgame）昨日正式上映，除了導演羅素兄弟早前發表公開信呼籲觀眾切勿劇透外，連MCL戲院亦在facebook專頁亦發文，籲觀眾遵守「睇戲禮儀」，再三提醒不要劇透，但仍然有人不顧勸告，四處惡意劇透，影響別人的觀影體驗。有網民在社交網站發文，指昨日在茶餐廳用膳時，有人無故以AirDrop劇透了《復仇者聯盟4》劇情。<br />\n<br />\n該網民在Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」發文，指昨日在茶餐廳用膳時，「有人無端端AirDrop我成篇關於Avengers 4整個劇情，好彩我睇咗啫」。<br />\n<br />\n根據其上傳的照片可見，有人將電影劇情的重點以文字交代，其後製成照片，再以AirDrop（無線傳輸功能）傳送予附近的陌生人。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言批評有關行為無公德心，直言「捉佢出嚟打啦！唔使原諒」，亦有人留言稱「咁算恐怖襲擊嗎？我依家打劫，快啲攞錢出來，唔係我就劇透！」、「已睇左，不過唔欣賞呢種share方式」。<br />\n<br />\n擔心被劇透的Marvel迷，記得要將自己的Airdrop設置成「關閉接收」或是「只限通訊錄聯絡人」，這樣就不會收到惡意劇透訊息了！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986929&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=bdcdf926\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986929&h=4cee3947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986929</a>"},{"pid":"e3d66f614918bb63c4f66b02d5fd07096e518cce","tid":1124713,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9S0qNQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9S0qNQ.png&h=4a3a1e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我已經獲得劇透保護</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacf37ea3e2e291cea00d1ade1af600b5e56e27e","tid":1124713,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"Thx<br />\n準備用依個方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d77fe29066fc0ed08fb12d54fb1ecde2cea248","tid":1124713,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"叫蘋果bam佢apple id<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}